		<title>澳元兌美元週二聚焦澳洲聯邦儲備銀行利率決定</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hant/analysis/market-news/audusd-rba-rate-decision</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 20 May 2025 04:13:15 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[市場新聞及觀點]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[AUDUSD]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[最近的新聞]]></category>
